  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/a80879395f0e43a58f3ea6f4db1a7ac8.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=216 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/1df020939c901bb382ec3b988562c549.webp?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=57 /></span><br>Immerse into a colourfully ambient space, effortlessly glide through each world, and find your moment of Zen.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Featuring</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>320</strong> handcrafted levels<br></li><li> Unique <strong>meditative</strong> gameplay<br></li><li> Multipul input methods, <strong>mouse</strong>, <strong>controller</strong>, <strong>touch</strong><br></li><li> Over <strong>two hours</strong> of play time<br></li><li> Over 1 hour of <strong>original music</strong><br></li><li> Breathing session <br></li><li> Cloud sync <br></li><li> Visual narrative<br></li><li> ‘<strong>Instagrammable</strong>’ content to share<br></li><li> Designed specifically to manifest <strong>relaxation</strong> and <strong>well being</strong></li></ul><br>Inspired by the Zen calligraphy practice of Ensô, where every day you paint an uninhibited ink circle on a blank sheet of paper.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Expressing a physical moment of reflection, focus, and freedom of flow.<br>Kanso is carefully balanced to invoke the flow of this calligraphic practice as a unique gameplay experience. <br>As you move around the circular forms, avoiding the Koi like Daemons, you will also find this flow, this moment of Zen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/3b6efc43b3561c9772c184adea895f6a.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/b68ac25b6e734a4974e53ac11e95cd09.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=251 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/b68ac25b6e734a4974e53ac11e95cd09.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/dedce345abdfc0274cd4dc226cd0c988.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>Navigate through ten worlds and explore over three hundred levels.<br>Each level with a different circular shape to follow and guiding energies to avoid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d66060a5acc6d753f53f70a4e5f5e121.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Move with each guiding energy, a Daemon following its own distinct movement pattern.  <br>Some follow you, others avoid you, all of them moving in predictable paths that gently draw you into a tranquil gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/70bf9286f2ff49208d6430d2315e68c0.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Along the player’s journey they will encounter our breathing session, a place where the Ensô breathes along with you while calming music is played. <br>Inspired by Resonant Breathing, the practice of slowing your breathing rate to approximately six breaths per minute. <br>Slowing your heart rate variability, and resulting in a calm, de-stressed state of mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/3b6efc43b3561c9772c184adea895f6a.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/11c92cb5112fc98a315ee2d3e76c1456.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>I created Kanso to be a place of beauty and refuge from the noise of daily life.  <br>To bring players of every skill level into a meditative state of flow.  Into an immersion of a calming experience. <br>I hope you'll join me and find your own moment of <strong>Zen</strong>.<br>:Dave",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/a80879395f0e43a58f3ea6f4db1a7ac8.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=216 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/1df020939c901bb382ec3b988562c549.webp?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=57 /></span><br>Immerse into a colourfully ambient space, effortlessly glide through each world, and find your moment of Zen.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Featuring</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>320</strong> handcrafted levels<br></li><li> Unique <strong>meditative</strong> gameplay<br></li><li> Multipul input methods, <strong>mouse</strong>, <strong>controller</strong>, <strong>touch</strong><br></li><li> Over <strong>two hours</strong> of play time<br></li><li> Over 1 hour of <strong>original music</strong><br></li><li> Breathing session <br></li><li> Cloud sync <br></li><li> Visual narrative<br></li><li> ‘<strong>Instagrammable</strong>’ content to share<br></li><li> Designed specifically to manifest <strong>relaxation</strong> and <strong>well being</strong></li></ul><br>Inspired by the Zen calligraphy practice of Ensô, where every day you paint an uninhibited ink circle on a blank sheet of paper.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/67940448b3c0af671f70ae3a22d56a31.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Expressing a physical moment of reflection, focus, and freedom of flow.<br>Kanso is carefully balanced to invoke the flow of this calligraphic practice as a unique gameplay experience. <br>As you move around the circular forms, avoiding the Koi like Daemons, you will also find this flow, this moment of Zen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/18a60039f017774f2fffab2bf46983ec.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/3b6efc43b3561c9772c184adea895f6a.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/b68ac25b6e734a4974e53ac11e95cd09.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=251 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/b68ac25b6e734a4974e53ac11e95cd09.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/dedce345abdfc0274cd4dc226cd0c988.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>Navigate through ten worlds and explore over three hundred levels.<br>Each level with a different circular shape to follow and guiding energies to avoid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d66060a5acc6d753f53f70a4e5f5e121.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d4de37fbf511ce43bb04c65cb82f6f70.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Move with each guiding energy, a Daemon following its own distinct movement pattern.  <br>Some follow you, others avoid you, all of them moving in predictable paths that gently draw you into a tranquil gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/70bf9286f2ff49208d6430d2315e68c0.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.poster.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.webm?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/d2d46fcfc3669a11bfd79efd81b1e611.mp4?t=1710686035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Along the player’s journey they will encounter our breathing session, a place where the Ensô breathes along with you while calming music is played. <br>Inspired by Resonant Breathing, the practice of slowing your breathing rate to approximately six breaths per minute. <br>Slowing your heart rate variability, and resulting in a calm, de-stressed state of mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/3b6efc43b3561c9772c184adea895f6a.avif?t=1710686035\" width=618 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454650/extras/11c92cb5112fc98a315ee2d3e76c1456.avif?t=1710686035\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>I created Kanso to be a place of beauty and refuge from the noise of daily life.  <br>To bring players of every skill level into a meditative state of flow.  Into an immersion of a calming experience. <br>I hope you'll join me and find your own moment of <strong>Zen</strong>.<br>:Dave",
